{"tid":145023,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]為ex設計一杯cocktail","createTime":"2017-03-06T02:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T06:42:13.000Z","uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f221a7777872d083e433558cdf511600fa5f63b","tid":145023,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:13:37.000Z","msg":"事源係，當年有為exexex exex設計左杯cocktail<br />\n<br />\n咁冇理由ex冇一杯屬於佢嘅cocktail嫁嘛<br />\n所以要公平啲，為佢諗返杯屬於佢嘅cocktail<br />\n<br />\n但小妹已經有成一年冇創作過signature cocktail，對酒嘅感覺已經冇左，咁就希望咁多位可以俾下意見<br />\n<br />\n放返張為exex創作嘅cocktail先<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tn05zu9c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftn05zu9c&h=007a1b82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢杯叫DOR Evil<br />\n正式係用Sailor Jerry spiced rum <br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以幫手諗下<br />\nTELEGRAM: KIMCHOW<br />\nINSTAGRAM: kcdrinkstube"},{"pid":"751c5882551adc47dedb330e863c524361d737ce","tid":145023,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:18:33.000Z","msg":"Whisky + Cabernet Sauvignon + Pineapple juice<br />\n利申 鳩up"},{"pid":"ed5fc1d837c1a53f8f2452f654b862db517fc07f","tid":145023,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Whisky + Cabernet Sauvignon + Pineapple juice<br />\n利申 鳩up</blockquote><br />\n唔記得左交代佢鍾意vodka<br />\n所以要用Vodka做base"},{"pid":"d2b586e5e6d3c00be27e1fb8e68577ecc423056f","tid":145023,"uid":66555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:26:44.000Z","msg":"long island iced tea 比例重設 + orange juice，lemon juice，pineapple juice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實驗下"},{"pid":"2eeadc923b5bf492c5090011e8264cd1c4b7702f","tid":145023,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Whisky + Cabernet Sauvignon + Pineapple juice<br />\n利申 鳩up</blockquote><br />\n唔記得左交代佢鍾意vodka<br />\n所以要用Vodka做base</blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得cocktail 呢啲野係要講感覺 唔同心情飲唔同既cocktail, 如果你想自制一杯 我覺得你不如試下有味道去形容你地曾經既關係 <br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999"},{"pid":"9f5d5f2115589b20f3a140dd77e617f988621bbc","tid":145023,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Whisky + Cabernet Sauvignon + Pineapple juice<br />\n利申 鳩up</blockquote><br />\n唔記得左交代佢鍾意vodka<br />\n所以要用Vodka做base</blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得cocktail 呢啲野係要講感覺 唔同心情飲唔同既cocktail, 如果你想自制一杯 我覺得你不如試下<span style=\"color: red;\">用</span>味道去形容你地曾經既關係 <br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f76a16e158b521843e8be903367db805710252c6","tid":145023,"uid":82704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:34:55.000Z","msg":"用6條mars chocolate bar infuse落一支vodka <br />\n加普洱<br />\n再加toasted marshmallow"},{"pid":"62600549b8010a114ca2e329c0fad308b184f2a6","tid":145023,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:53:35.000Z","msg":"五加皮、雙蒸、豆漿、廿四味涼茶、維他奶溝埋，再打隻龜蛋落去攪勻，再加多滴墨汁"},{"pid":"c75313f9bfb293ef639fe6e10e7d3f93c4c24282","tid":145023,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五加皮、雙蒸、豆漿、廿四味涼茶、維他奶溝埋，再打隻龜蛋落去攪勻，再加多滴墨汁</blockquote><br />\n我沖俾你飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8489e4a0b55a5b972ae0e03df005e183feead7f0","tid":145023,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"雲吞兩粒，加一盒麥精<br />\n<br />\n大火煲半個鐘"},{"pid":"2722907acc9c40b1ce8dbb1ccaf82acbb39a334b","tid":145023,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">long island iced tea</span> 比例重設 + orange juice，lemon juice，pineapple juice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實驗下</blockquote><br />\n拿來長島冰茶換我半晚安睡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk